### ==========================================
### BADWALLET SYSTEM - TEST REQUESTS
### ==========================================

### 1. Seeder - Crée 10 wallets
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/seed
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Créer un wallet
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phoneNumber": "771234567",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "initialBalance": 100000,
    "pinCode": "1234",
    "currency": "XOF"
}

### 3. Récupérer la liste des wallets (COPIER UN ID ICI)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallets?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Détails d'un wallet (utilise le téléphone)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/771234567
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Consulter le solde (utilise le téléphone)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/771234567/balance
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Dépôt (REMETTRE L'ID COPIÉ À L'ÉTAPE 3)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/{ID_COPIÉ}/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 50000,
    "source": "CREDIT_CARD"
}

### 7. Retrait (REMETTRE L'ID COPIÉ)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": "{ID_COPIÉ}",
    "amount": 25000
}

### 8. Retrait frais max (REMETTRE L'ID COPIÉ)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": "{ID_COPIÉ}",
    "amount": 600000
}

### 9. Transfert (REMETTRE L'ID COPIÉ)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sourceWalletId": "{ID_COPIÉ}",
    "targetPhoneNumber": "7700000002",
    "amount": 15000
}

### 10. Historique des transactions (utilise le téléphone)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/771234567/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Paiement ISM (REMETTRE L'ID COPIÉ)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": "{ID_COPIÉ}",
    "phoneNumber": "771234567",
    "provider": "ISM"
}

### 12. Paiement WOYAFAL (REMETTRE L'ID COPIÉ)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": "{ID_COPIÉ}",
    "phoneNumber": "771234567",
    "provider": "WOYAFAL"
}

### 13. Paiement multiple (REMETTRE L'ID COPIÉ)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallets/pay-factures
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": "{ID_COPIÉ}",
    "invoiceReferences": ["BILL-ISM-771234567-2026-June", "BILL-WOYAFAL-771234567-2026-June"]
}

### 14. Factures impayées ISM
GET http://localhost:8080/api/external/factures/771234567/current?provider=ISM
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. Factures impayées WOYAFAL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/external/factures/771234567/current?provider=WOYAFAL
Content-Type: application/json

### 16. Factures par période
GET http://localhost:8080/api/external/factures/771234567/periode?debut=2026-01-01&fin=2026-12-31
Content-Type: application/json


### ==========================================
### payment-service (Port 8081)
### ==========================================

### 1. Générer les factures
POST http://localhost:8081/api/bills/generate/771234567
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Facture courante ISM
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills/current/771234567?provider=ISM
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Facture courante WOYAFAL
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills/current/771234567?provider=WOYAFAL
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Factures par période
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills/period/771234567?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Factures par références
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills/references?references=BILL-ISM-771234567-2026-June,BILL-WOYAFAL-771234567-2026-June
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Marquer ISM payée
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/bills/BILL-ISM-771234567-2026-June/pay?transactionReference=TXN-123456
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Marquer WOYAFAL payée
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/bills/BILL-WOYAFAL-771234567-2026-June/pay?transactionReference=TXN-123457
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Liste de toutes les factures
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Factures par téléphone
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills/phone/771234567
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Factures impayées
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills/unpaid/771234567
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Détail d'une facture
GET http://localhost:8081/api/bills/BILL-ISM-771234567-2026-June
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. Créer une facture
POST http://localhost:8081/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phoneNumber": "771234567",
    "provider": "ISM",
    "amount": 50000,
    "month": "July",
    "year": "2026",
    "description": "ISM bill for July 2026"
}

### 13. Générer pour tous
POST http://localhost:8081/api/bills/generate/all
Content-Type: application/json

["771234567", "778765432", "776543210"]

### 14. Vérifier facture payée (doit retourner 500 ou erreur)
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/bills/BILL-ISM-771234567-2026-May/pay?transactionReference=TXN-999999
Content-Type: application/json